# Random Forest, Boosting & ROC Analysis

This repository contains the Python implementation and presentation materials for **RF Project** of the Applied Machine Learning course. The project explores ensemble learning techniques (Random Forest and Gradient Boosting) and evaluates classification thresholds using Receiver Operating Characteristic (ROC) curves.

---

## 📁 Repository Structure

```text
├── KPI_data_for_logit_model.csv   # Dataset used for modeling
├── 4-RF-Boosting.ipynb            # Main Jupyter Notebook containing code & analysis
├── 4-RF-Boosting.pptx             # Summary presentation slides
├── 3-CART.ipynb                   # Previous lab notebook (CART reference)
├── 3-CART.pptx                    # Previous lab presentation slides
└── README.md                      # Project documentation
